在旺角彌敦道及亞皆老街的集會地點，約在下午2時開始，有大批反佔中示威者到達旺角，且人數是示威者的數倍。反佔中示威者四出挑釁指罵和推撞，不斷拆毁在場的帳篷及路障，並追打集會人士。他們亦不時向集會人士和在場記者投擲雜物<ref name="蘋果日報20141003">{{cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52975934 |title=【佔領旺角】反佔中暴徒湧現 撐學生市民反包圍 |publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]] |date=2014-10-03 |accessdate=2014-10-03 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006035054/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52975934 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。集會人士批評警方並未有效地阻止反佔中人士的襲擊<ref name="蘋果日報20141003" />。有市民得知警方未有阻止反佔中人士的暴行，在下班後趕到現場，希望保護和支持現場學生<ref name="蘋果日報20141003" />。另一方面，[[愛港之聲|愛港之聲]]召集人[[陳淨心|陳淨心]]在Facebook專頁留言，指「情況危急，緊急召集熱血之仕」，呼籲民眾晚上6點在旺角雅蘭商場集合，到旺角清除鐵馬，並將行動命名為「光復香港」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%99%B3%E6%B7%A8%E5%BF%83%E3%80%8C%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8D%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC6%E6%99%82%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%8B%86%E9%90%B5%E9%A6%AC/web_tc/article/20141003/s00001/1412326243740|title=陳淨心「光復香港」號召6時旺角拆鐵馬|publisher=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=2014-10-03|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006124832/http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%99%B3%E6%B7%A8%E5%BF%83%E3%80%8C%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8D%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC6%E6%99%82%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%8B%86%E9%90%B5%E9%A6%AC/web_tc/article/20141003/s00001/1412326243740|dead-url=no}}</ref>

到傍晚，反佔中人士不斷增多。警員在安全考慮下，將停留在彌敦道多日的巴士由司機駛出，並開路協助集會人士離開。期間有集會人士被在場的反佔中示威者追打及挑釁指罵，警員隨即加派人員控制場面，集會者斥警方並無有效地阻止反佔中暴徒的行為。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52975934|title=【佔領旺角】反佔中暴徒湧現 撐學生市民反包圍|publisher=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=2014-10-03|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006035054/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52975934|dead-url=no}}</ref>但由於現時大批反佔中人士繼續包圍集會人士，現場不時有打鬥事件。混亂中至少兩名男子頭部受傷。其中一名男子被人打至頭破血流，由警員扶到港鐵站出口。被打傷至頭部流血的男子稱，他在十字路口被反佔中人士襲擊，過程約十秒<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%20%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%8D%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%93%E5%82%B7/web_tc/article/20141003/s00001/1412340611553 |title=示威者流血 稱被反佔中人士打傷 |publisher=[[明報|明報]] |date=2014-10-03 |accessdate=2014-10-03 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006171205/http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%20%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%8D%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%93%E5%82%B7/web_tc/article/20141003/s00001/1412340611553 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他表示，自己支持學生，到場保護學生，期間被十多人包圍，頭部再被腳踢。他批評警方完全不執法，漠視市民安全，指警方助長暴力，揚言一定會追究。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52976521|title=【佔領旺角】雨傘革命支持者被打爆頭|publisher=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=2014-10-03|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006031554/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52976521|dead-url=no}}</ref>而佩戴藍絲帶的示威者情緒激動，大喊：「清場！清場！」、「打死他！」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/socrec/photos/a.593110604049208.152616.160696287290644/984410784919186/?type=1&theater|title=旺角佔領現場|publisher=[[SocREC_社會記錄頻道|SocREC 社會記錄頻道]]|date=2014-10-03|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-date=2018-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509094658/https://www.facebook.com/socrec/photos/a.593110604049208.152616.160696287290644/984410784919186/?type=1&theater|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[香港記者協會|香港記者協會]]指，有女記者在旺角採訪反佔中與佔中示威者衝突時，遭一名男子用硬物敲打手臂。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%89%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2/web_tc/article/20141004/s00001/1412353641241|title=記協指有記者旺角遇襲|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|date=2014-10-04|accessdate=2014-10-04|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006152118/http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%89%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2/web_tc/article/20141004/s00001/1412353641241|dead-url=no}}</ref>

多家外國傳媒的報道均稱該些反佔中示威者為「暴徒」 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2780380/Mobs-linked-TRIAD-gangs-try-drive-Hong-Kongs-pro-democracy-protesters-streets-demostrations-turn-running-brawls.html|title=Mobs linked to TRIAD gangs try to drive Hong Kong's pro-democracy protesters off the streets as demonstrations turn into running brawls|work=[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]|date=2014-10-03|access-date=2015-08-22|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924185342/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2780380/Mobs-linked-TRIAD-gangs-try-drive-Hong-Kongs-pro-democracy-protesters-streets-demostrations-turn-running-brawls.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/03/hong-kong-talks-cancelled-after-pro-china-mobs-attack-protesters-in-the-streets/|title=Hong Kong talks cancelled after pro-China mobs attack protesters in the streets|work=加拿大[[國家郵報|國家郵報]]|date=2014-10-03|access-date=2015-08-22|archive-date=2015-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322052946/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/03/hong-kong-talks-cancelled-after-pro-china-mobs-attack-protesters-in-the-streets/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2014/10/03/hong-kongs-battle-lines-harden-after-mob-attacks-protesters/|title=Hong Kong’s battle lines harden after mob attacks protesters|date=2014-10-03|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|access-date=2015-08-22|archive-date=2014-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141125002258/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2014/10/03/hong-kongs-battle-lines-harden-after-mob-attacks-protesters/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ireport.cnn.com/docs/DOC-1175911 |title=Anti-Occupy Mob |access-date=2015-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021035240/http://ireport.cnn.com/docs/DOC-1175911 |archive-date=2014-10-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而佔中示威者亦稱，若警方不阻止反佔中人士的暴力行為，就會終止與政府的對話<ref name="明報20141003_18:39">{{cite web |url=http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%20%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B7%E8%88%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%80-%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E6%96%A5%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%8F%8D%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%98%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92/web_tc/article/20141003/s00001/1412332769934 |title=佔中學聯：不制止暴力 將中斷與政府對話 |publisher=[[明報|明報]] |date=2014-10-03 |accessdate=2014-10-03 |archive-date=2014-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141005195046/http://news2.mingpao.com/ins/%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%20%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B7%E8%88%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%80-%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E6%96%A5%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%8F%8D%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%98%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92/web_tc/article/20141003/s00001/1412332769934 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。和平佔中和學聯宣布棄守旺角，往金鐘集會現場，但無人理會。佔中發起人之一戴耀廷呼籲旺角集會人士離開，到金鐘互相守護。學聯副秘書長岑敖暉表示「不想（集會人士）流任何一滴血同有任何傷害」，呼籲於旺角集會人士遇傷害時要立即撤離<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52975794 |title=【雨傘革命】戴耀廷籲棄守旺角 學聯疑暴徒為有背景人士 |publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]] |date=2014-10-03 |accessdate=2014-10-03 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006035044/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141003/52975794 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。學民思潮發言人[[周庭|周庭]]亦呼籲佔中支持者盡快離開旺角<ref name="明報20141003_18:39" />。有佔中示威者不滿警方沒有及時制止反佔中人士發起的「自發清場」暴力行動 ，有網民隨即在Facebook開設一個「反佔中暴徒認人組」，收集圖片、影片，希望能找出施暴者，然後交警方處理。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.facebook.com/pages/%E5%8F%8D%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%B5%84/542698572527095?ref=notif&notif_t=fbpage_fan_invite|title=反佔中暴徒認人組|date=2014-10-04|accessdate=2015-08-22|archive-date=2022-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513100025/https://www.facebook.com/pages/%E5%8F%8D%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%B5%84/542698572527095?ref=notif&notif_t=fbpage_fan_invite}}</ref>

