學聯對政府的回應表示質疑，認為實質作用不大<ref>{{cite news|title=政府擬向中央提交民情報告及構建政改多方平台|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/政府擬向中央提交民情報告及構建政改多方平台-125000393.html|publisher=商業電台|language=zh|accessdate=2021-07-08|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305213825/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%B0%91%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%8F%8A%E6%A7%8B%E5%BB%BA%E6%94%BF%E6%94%B9%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-125000393.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=政府指民锖報告會盡量客觀|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/政府指民锖報告會盡量客觀-123000746.html|publisher=商業電台|language=zh|accessdate=2021-07-08|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305204539/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87%E6%B0%91%E9%94%96%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%AE%A2%E8%A7%80-123000746.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=政府承諾交民情報告建多方平台|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/政府承諾交民情報告建多方平台-134145687.html|publisher=Now.com|language=zh|accessdate=2021-07-08|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305195720/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E4%BA%A4%E6%B0%91%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%BB%BA%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-134145687.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

政府深夜發出聲明，稱政府「懷着最大的誠意與學聯的同學代表就政制發展進行了兩小時坦誠和有意義的對話，政府並提出了4點回應。惟得悉學聯認為政府無給予實際回應，就此政府表示失望」。學聯批評，政府向中央提交的政改報告不全面，最終令人大落閘。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115618|title=學聯及政府就政改進行首次對話|work=[[now新聞|now新聞]]|date=2014-10-21|accessdate=2014-10-21|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807123000/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115618|dead-url=no}}</ref>

鄭國漢再次承諾，會不偏不倚主持會議，期望對話可拉近雙方距離。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115549|title=鄭國漢冀對話拉近雙方距離|work=[[now新聞|now新聞]]|date=2014-10-21|accessdate=2014-10-20|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807123148/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115549|dead-url=no}}</ref>行政長官梁振英星期一在禮賓府接受外地傳媒訪問時表示，行政長官候選人須經提名委員會產生，不應該只追求人數多，否則香港會步向福利主義。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115548|title=梁振英：提委會求人多 港會步向福利主義|work=[[now新聞|now新聞]]|date=2014-10-21|accessdate=2014-10-20|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807123121/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115548|dead-url=no}}</ref>難以期望一次對話解決問題，政府抱最大誠意聆聽學生意見。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115566|title=梁振英：政府抱最大誠意聆聽學生意見|work=[[now新聞|now新聞]]|date=2014-10-21|accessdate=2014-10-20|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807123258/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115566|dead-url=no}}</ref>

